P ¼ R†XT Y if rankðRÞ o m

ð19Þ

in which the R† is the pseudoinverse of R.
 Step 4: Construct the ﬁnal model of MPLSR:

Y ¼ XP þ Ey

ð20Þ

in which Ey is the residual part of Y that is uncorrelated with X.

