Yandong Yang is serving as a professor in Bohai University, Liaoning, China. He has authored or coauthored 5 books and more than 20 peer-reviewed journal papers. His research interests include human resource management and logistics.
Congzhou Yu is currently pursuing the B.Sc. degree in the College of Education and P.E., Bohai University, Liaoning, China. His main research interest is logistics.

